snippet.title: Brilliant Albert Einstein Quotes #shorts
snippet.description:
Brilliant Albert Einstein Quotes #shorts

Albert Einstein was a German-born theoretical physicist, widely acknowledged to be one of the greatest physicists of all time. Einstein is best known for developing the theory of relativity, but he also made important contributions to the development of the theory of quantum mechanics.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Albert Einstein. The best quotes and aphorisms of Albert Einstein that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Albert Einstein are definitely worth your time.

Thank you for watching!
